disableParam_NT.Wiki: Parameters marked with are excluded in the NT version package.

unlockFlagId.Wiki: Lifting flag (default 0). If this event flag is set, the ban will be lifted (displayed on the loading screen). If it is 0, the ban is always lifted. The invalid flag has priority

invalidFlagId.Wiki: Invalid flag (default 0). If this event flag is set, it will be disabled (it will not be displayed on the loading screen). If it is 0, this flag is not always set.

msgId.Wiki: Text ID (Loading Text.xlsx). Used for both loading titles and loading text
